Dhoondhe har ik saans me
Dubkiyon ke baad me
Har bhanvar ke paas kinare
Beh rahe jo sath me
Jo hamare khaas the
Kar gaye apni baat kinareGar maajhi saare sath me
Gair ho bhi jaayein
To khud hi to patvaar ban
Paar honge hum
Jo chhoti si har ik nehar
Sagar ban bhi jaaye
Koi tinka leke hath me
Dhoondh lenge hum kinaare
